description: A humorous punchline about a mountain climber's son.
title: Cliff
n_1: Dad and Son are hiking on a mountain trail.
c1_1: Hey, what did the mountain climber name his son?
n_2: Dad grins as he gets ready to deliver the punchline.
n_3: They both laugh together at the joke.
n_4: Dad and Son continue their hike, smiling.
